captions.text:
Time to play, ladies and gentlemen,
the favorite game

of any woman caught cheating
on her husband: "Quick Change"!

Elidio, Daniel and Rabin,
let's play "Quick Change"!

It works like this: They will play a scene
and every time I say 'change'!

they will have to change
the last thing they said.

You, in green, who said
it was your first time here.

There's something in my hand!
Everybody's seeing it!
You're gonna tell me what it is!

- A bottle.
- A bottle! Give it up for her!

It's a bottle.
See? A bottle.
I'll give the bottle to Elidio.

A bottle will start the
"Quick Change" game,

Hey dad...
Can I drink some juice?

-But I don't want it, I want beer!
-Change!

I have to hide all the
bottles in this house...

- Child Protective Services
shows up here again... - Change!

- Adult Protective Services
shows up here again... - Change!

Elderly Protective Services
shows up here again...
What if they find the bottles?

- They can't find this stuff
in my house! - Change!

- They can't find this kind of thing
in my house! - Change!
They can't drink anything here, got it?

Agent Thompson!
I'm from... Elderly Stuff.

It seems an elderly child is here...
Drinking.

-Really? Then what's that hand behind you?
- Change!

- What'sthat other hand behind you?
- Change!

What are these two hands 
and a feet behind you?

You scared me! For a moment
I thought you were a perpetrator!

We heard about a
human being living here!
Are you trying to warn me of something?
